  "text": "The transmitter architecture is the same as the previous work [CITATION_1] , as shown in Fig. 1 . The carrier frequency of the system is controlled by the oscillator in the transmitter. In the experiment, the carrier frequency is set to 4 GHz. The bandwidth of the radar waveform is 500 MHz, making the system an ultra-wideband system.",
